author: Charlie Ridgely
title: 5 Great MCU Characters You Totally Forgot About
text:
5 Great MCU Characters You Totally Forgot About Charlie Ridgely Start Slideshow Slide of 
The Marvel Cinematic Universe continues to grow each and every year, and this means more and more characters are entering the fold. Since very few have been killed off, it's easy to forget exactly who has come and gone since 2008. 
While not everyone is Tony Stark or Peter Quill, the MCU has succeeded in creating some great characters. A few of these never got to achieve their full potential however, as they found themselves overshadowed by new additions to the franchise. 
We've taken some time to look at a few of these characters that aren't exactly around at the moment, but who's presence is sorely missed. 
The character's we've listed here are all still alive in the MCU, and could all make a comeback as the franchise heads into Phase 4.
